25
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,500
Yi Qing.

26
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,100
How is she doing?

27
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,540
Are you free?

28
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,020
Let's meet up.

29
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,160
Okay.

30
