41
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:01,420
of my life.

42
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,620
Your voice...

43
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:07,340
Are you okay?

44
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:11,580
Be good and take a seat.

45
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:15,920
Take a seat.

46
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:19,160
Just enjoy

47
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:21,180
